            "rating": 5,
            "title": "Didn't Expect It to Work THIS Well!",
            "quote": "\"I was not expecting this! When I laid down on the smoothspine massager, I could feel my back start to decompress in a good way. The heat and massage combined made a huge difference, and I could actually relax for the first time in months. My wife said I'm walking more upright. Definitely worth it trying!!\"",
