            "title": "I Can Move Freely Again!",
            "quote": "\"Ok, mine got here last week. I was skeptical at first, but after just a few sessions, my stiffness and sciatica pain improved drastically. I used to dread getting out of bed in the morning because of the pain, but now I can move freely again. So easy to use, and the heat feels amazing on my lower back.\"",
